4. Conditional Routing Logic
✔ Answer if:
Confidence > 0.7
Context available
🚨 Escalate if:
Confidence < 0.5
No relevant chunks
Complex/multi-part query



5. HITL Design
When Triggered:
Low confidence
Missing context
Flow:
Query sent to human dashboard
Human writes response
Response stored
Returned to user


